messages.content:
Step-by-step reasoning:

1. Detect a COC event DFON from Kitchen Lights device. When this happens, send a command to Hall Master to turn on with On Level 50% and Ramp Rate 2 minutes (which corresponds to enum 10).

2. Monitor Thermostat Temperature property (COS). If it rises above 78°F, send command to Thermostat to set Fan Mode to On (enum 1).

3. Detect COC DFON from ZW 006 Dimmer Switch (simulate double-click). When detected, send Brighten command to Kitchen Lights with parameter 20% (increase brightness by 20%).

4. Check if Hue Lily outdoor spotlight 7 is reachable (property Reachable == True) and Status == 0 (off). If so, send On command with parameters to set Color Temperature to 3500K and Brightness 200. Since the On command does not take parameters, we use Set Temp and Brightness command [SET_CTBR] with parameters Color Temperature=3500, Transition Time=0 (instant), Brightness=200.

5. Detect COS change of Thermostat Mode property to Heat (enum 1). When this happens, send command to Thermostat to set Heat Setpoint to 72°F.

No nested ifs, each routine is separate.

---

{
  "automation": [
    {
      "name": "Kitchen Lights Physical On triggers Hall Master 50%",
      "condition": {
        "==": {
          "device": "Kitchen Lights",
          "coc": "DFON"
        }
      },
      "action": {
        "device": "Hall Master",
        "command": "On Level",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "On Level", "value": 50, "uom": "percent", "precision": 1 }
        ]
      },
      "additional_action": {
        "device": "Hall Master",
        "command": "Ramp Rate",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "Ramp Rate", "value": 10, "uom": "enum", "precision": 0 }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Thermostat temperature above 78F turns fan on",
      "condition": {
        ">": {
          "device": "Thermostat",
          "status": "Temperature",
          "value": 78,
          "uom": "fahrenheit",
          "precision": 1
        }
      },
      "action": {
        "device": "Thermostat",
        "command": "Fan Mode",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "Fan Mode", "value": 1, "uom": "enum", "precision": 0 }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "ZW 006 Dimmer Switch double-click brightens Kitchen Lights",
      "condition": {
        "==": {
          "device": "ZW 006 Dimmer Switch",
          "coc": "DFON"
        }
      },
      "action": {
        "device": "Kitchen Lights",
        "command": "Brighten",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "Level", "value": 20, "uom": "percent", "precision": 1 }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Turn on Hue Lily spotlight with color temp and brightness if reachable and off",
      "condition": {
        "and": [
          {
            "==": {
              "device": "Hue Lily outdoor spotlight 7",
              "status": "Reachable",
              "value": 1,
              "uom": "enum",
              "precision": 0
            }
          },
          {
            "==": {
              "device": "Hue Lily outdoor spotlight 7",
              "status": "Status",
              "value": 0,
              "uom": "percent",
              "precision": 1
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "action": {
        "device": "Hue Lily outdoor spotlight 7",
        "command": "Set Temp and Brightness",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "Color Temperature", "value": 3500, "uom": "kelvin", "precision": 1 },
          { "name": "Transition Time", "value": 0, "uom": "millisecond", "precision": 1 },
          { "name": "Brightness", "value": 200, "uom": "level", "precision": 1 }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Set Heat Setpoint to 72F when Thermostat mode changes to Heat",
      "condition": {
        "==": {
          "device": "Thermostat",
          "status": "Mode",
          "value": 1,
          "uom": "enum",
          "precision": 0
        }
      },
      "action": {
        "device": "Thermostat",
        "command": "Heat Setpoint",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "Heat Setpoint", "value": 72, "uom": "fahrenheit", "precision": 1 }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
